{"tid":126460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"團體要求政府正視學生自殺","createTime":"2017-02-19T11:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T16:00:06.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c3b68914e42547f0693093bbfc7d2501a351d8f","tid":126460,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】有團體向政府請願，要求正視學生自殺問題。<br />\n防止學生自殺民間聯席，包括立法會議員邵家臻和張超雄等十多人在政府總部外，先為今年五名輕生的學生默哀。<br />\n他們質疑政府的防止學生自殺委員會未能根治問題，又批評政府推行BCA，即改良版TSA，是漠視民意，要求政務司司長張建宗成立高層次跨部門小組檢討教育系統。<br />\n團體稍後亦會逐一跟各特首參選人會面，要求籌組班子時任命有質素的教育局局長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/團體要求政府正視學生自殺-032542082.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%96%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA-032542082.html&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6r%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=35d628d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/團體要求政府正視學生自殺-032542082.html</a>"},{"pid":"e02a0ef71cfaf6ad471089a69c7fac232d8eaf35","tid":126460,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:24:01.000Z","msg":"出得世 預左嫁啦 正咩視"},{"pid":"3bd639605e0c688bbc2bd80073448df3c9266c15","tid":126460,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:36:07.000Z","msg":"吳克檢做左咁耐有幾多個學生自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />??"},{"pid":"f3e1c5f457b03d87bd99e86efc19d54c6e7f317d","tid":126460,"uid":56627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:38:11.000Z","msg":"班賤民自殺關皇帝撚事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f58cfbc27ff1f6f94c725f8c95f65a0741d878","tid":126460,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:43:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ae8f8e5eee18746dc429ca